ğŸ¯ Problem Statement

The objective of this project is to predict whether a customer will subscribe to a term deposit based on demographic, financial, and campaign-related attributes.

This is a binary classification problem, where:

deposit = yes â†’ Customer subscribed

deposit = no â†’ Customer did not subscribe

ğŸ’¼ Business Context & Relevance

Direct marketing campaigns are costly and time-intensive. Accurately predicting which customers are more likely to subscribe allows the bank to:

Reduce operational costs

Improve campaign efficiency

Increase conversion rates

Optimize customer targeting

A reliable predictive model can significantly improve marketing ROI.

