âš  Key Observations & Modeling Considerations
ğŸš¨ Data Leakage Risk

The feature duration represents call duration and is known only after the call is completed.

Including it in modeling may cause unrealistic performance.

Recommendation:

Build models both with and without duration.

âš– Class Imbalance

Potential bias toward majority class.
Solutions:

SMOTE

Class weighting

Stratified sampling

ğŸ“‰ Skewed Features

Log transformation recommended for:

balance

duration

